title: Gelish: Mini UV Light 1
description: Great for Home or Travel. mini Light cures polish for a long lasting manicure Gelish Mini Light is designed to cure Gelish Gel Polish to ensure a complete cure so the colors are completely dry and have a high shine. Cures Mini Foundation in 1 Minute, Mini Gelish Colors in 2 - 3 minutes, and Mini Top It Off in 2 minutes. The Mini Light is great for those on the go or to do a quick touch up and be dry in just minutes. The small and compact size makes it great for travel to ensure the perfect Gelish Gel Polish all the time. Requires four AA batteries (not included). Available AC Power Cord & Adapter (sold seprately).
